summary:
American School of Paris, Class of 2020. 

Communication student, with a passion for media, Podcast host  

Inquisitive & creative personality, engaged, dynamic and likes to contribute to projects with innovative ideas. 
Multicultural background gained from having lived in diverse locations (Switzerland, US and France). Apt to see beyond cultural clichés and ability to understand others’ perspective.
Excellent oral communication and presentation skills.
Fluent in French, Spanish and English.
